definition: square/power or involution (math.)/upright/honest/fair and square/direction/side/party (to a contract, dispute etc)/place/method/prescription (medicine)/just when/only or just/classifier for square things/abbr. for square or cubic meter

sentences.english: So where does this lead us?
sentences.chinese: 那么，它将带领我们走向何方？

sentences.english: Unfortunately a lot of people still don't know where it is.
sentences.chinese: 但遗憾的是，仍有很多人不知道香港地处何方。

sentences.english: It is far away in the country, but always with me,wherever I am.
sentences.chinese: 它虽远在乡下，但不论我身在何方，它都会伴随着我。

sentences.english: It should be clear where this path leads.
sentences.chinese: 这条道路通向何方应该是一目了然的。

sentences.english: Don't run through life so fast that you forget not only where you've been, but also where you are going.
sentences.chinese: 不要过怏地穿越生活而遗忘了你身在何处，将向何方。

sentences.english: Where do community organizers come from?
Where should Jingdezhen go in the future?
sentences.chinese: 景德镇的未来应该走向何方？

sentences.english: But Domenicali insists he is thinking dispassionately about what road to take.
sentences.chinese: 但是多梅尼力卡说自己正在冷静思考路在何方。

sentences.english: Where do things stand in the fight to raise the debt ceiling?
sentences.chinese: 提高债务上限之争，路向何方？

sentences.english: Where do you see the movement going?
sentences.chinese: 在你看来，这场运动将走向何方？

sentences.english: My music shows ye have your doses.
sentences.chinese: 但音乐却表明你将归去何方。

sentences.english: But where is the silver chariot headed?
sentences.chinese: 但那驾银制马车将前往何方？

sentences.english: And let me heartache is that the people, he is now in which direction?
sentences.chinese: 而属于那个让我心痛的人，他现在在何方？

sentences.english: Where will new innovations come from?
Where are the islands on which the immortals lived?
sentences.chinese: 神仙居住的蓬莱岛究竟在何方？

sentences.english: But just who is this 6) goddess of 7) homemaking?
sentences.chinese: 可是，这位居家生活女神到底是何方神圣？

definition: what course to follow/what path to take
not to know/unaware/unknowingly/fig. not to admit (defeat, hardships, tiredness etc)
the other end of the world/a faraway place
